# Vercel deploys the unified Next.js host at
# `04-the-final-portal/milesymedia-website/` (chapter #122 unification —
# replaces the legacy `portal/` + `milesymedia website/` split + the
# old build-portal.mjs copy step). vercel.json's buildCommand cd's
# into that folder + runs `npm install && npm run build`.
# Per-client portals at `04-the-final-portal/clients/<slug>/` deploy as
# SEPARATE Vercel projects (one per Live client) — this file isn't
# read for those.

# Reference codebases — archived, not part of any deployment.
